==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Turcoman
<hw>Tur"co*man</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>pr. n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Turcomans</plw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>.</plu> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A member of
a tribe of Turanians inhabiting a region east of the Caspian
Sea.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A Turcoman carpet.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><mcol><col><b>Turcoman carpet</b></col> <it>or</it>
<col><b>Turcoman rug</b></col></mcol>, <cd>a kind of carpet or rug
supposed to be made by the Turcomans.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Turdiformes</ent>⟦br⟧
